must have things in ur vanity for freelancer makeup artist .
1) wire board 
2)twintape 
3)travel friendly light 
4)scissors 
5) blowdry brush
6) earburd
7) facerazor , tread 
8) nail paint / fake nail extensions (if client ask for it ) 
8) gluedrop 
9) brush cleanser for blenders coz we cant keep 5 6 blender 
10) instant brush spray ( if u want to use other colour with same brush ) .
